snippet.title: Sugar Shack - Official Trailer | Publisher Spotlight Showcase 2023 (Freedom Games)
snippet.description: Tap maple, farm, and open the Sugar Shack in this trailer for the upcoming maple syrup management game and world crafter set in a cozy, magical forest inspired by Quebec lore and art. Sugar Shack is coming to PC.
